description.en:
Rowket Market Is A Decentralized Community-Driven NFTs Marketplace Centered Around The Distribution Of Fan Art In The Form Of NFTs

$KET is the native currency of our marketplace where users will be able to mint, buy/sell NFTs. 

$KET is also a deflationary instant yield token with an adjustable tax rate of 3% on transactions which will give a 1% frictionless yield to hodlers and burns the other 2% for an ever-increasing price floor.
